eed support with advanced download filters (incl. regex) Many Bittorrent extensions supported Remote control through Web user interface, written with AJAX Sequential downloading (Download in order) Advanced control over torrents, trackers and peers Bandwidth scheduler Torrent creation tool IP Filtering (eMule & PeerGuardian format compatible) IPv6 compliant UPnP / NAT-PMP port forwarding support Available on all platforms: Windows, Linux, macOS, FreeBSD, OS/2 Available in ~70 languageskscreenshotsäxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/qbittorrent/qBittorrent/cc851d3ec33d7f7311d2a4ca4d807c0b/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/qbittorrent/qBittorrent/cc851d3ec33d7f7311d2a4ca4d807c0b/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/qbittorrent/qBittorrent/cc851d3ec33d7f7311d2a4ca4d807c0b/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/qbittorrent/qBittorrent/cc851d3ec33d7f7311d2a4ca4d807c0b/screenshots/image-4_orig.pnggversione5.0.2ldownload_urlxyhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v123-20250627052556/qbittorrent-27_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizei128.26 MBdbsumx@b1e8cc5bc62f8e7c309566ba46cf588a5f9ad14be7df006703250c5ac23eb55dfshasumx@d6e232a50d89cd469cd5a7d1dbcf620418d6b6d3fc15b3699bd68c33cc435271jbuild_datex2025-06-27 00:00:00 +0000 UTCjcategoriesxNetwork,FileTransfer,P2P»cpkgwmousepad.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namehMousepadfpkg_idxBgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.org.xfce.mousepad-27_06_2025-xplshnfapp_idqorg.xfce.mousepaddiconxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/xfce/mousepad/e80f32822455cb1a3096d8600c76608f/icons/128x128/org.xfce.mousepad.pngkdescriptionxAMousepad is a simple text editor for the Xfce desktop environmentpdescription_longyºMousepad aims to be an easy-to-use and fast editor. Our target is an editor for quickly editing text files, not a development environment or an editor with a huge bunch of plugins. On the other hand we try to use the latest GTK features available, which means t